ovides a natural solution to the puzzle of efficient information flow in the highly modular structure of the brain.","publicationCount":0,"publicationCountByYear":[],"citationCnt":0,"citationCountByYear":[],"rank":23240.0,"entityType":0},"dataVersion":"2019-01-11-prod"}